    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cutting tools consisting of a heavy blade with a hooked point fitted with a handle and used in pruning, clearning heavy brush, and maintaining hedges. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
